welcome_message_body: Welcome to Rockville, a charming city known for its historic charm, vibrant arts scene, and beautiful parks. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer during your visit.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Tipton AAF Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The smallest terminal at DCA, serving primarily regional flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: The main terminal at DCA, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal D
terminals.description: A newer terminal at DCA, serving primarily American Airlines flights.

wifi.note: Limited to 45 minutes per session. Premium options available for purchase.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at BWI handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A primarily serves Southwest Airlines and a few other domestic carriers.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is mainly used by American Airlines and its regional partners.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is primarily used by Delta Air Lines and its regional partners.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Frederick Municipal Airport is a small, single-story building that houses ticket counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Frederick Municipal Airport is a separate building used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal buildings.
